[0.003338, "o", "\r\n╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n"]
[0.00356, "o", "║  STAGE 3 — Z-machine runs on QB2 RISC-V cores  (TT-Lang)  ║\r\n╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
[2.004121, "o", "The interpreter kernel (kernels/zork_interpreter_l1.cpp) runs\r\ndirectly on the RISC-V cores embedded in the Blackhole chip.\r\nThe game file lives in DRAM. The cores do the Z-machine work.\r\n\r\nFirmware limits each kernel invocation to 10 instructions.\r\nWe open a fresh device session per batch to stay within limits.\r\n\r\n"]
[5.005365, "o", "Running 20 batches × 10 instructions = 200 Z-machine instructions...\r\n(Each batch: open device → load state → execute → save state → close device)\r\n\r\n"]
[8.133284, "o", "\u001b[32m2026-04-23 16:48:56.045\u001b[0m | \u001b[34m\u001b[1mDEBUG   \u001b[0m | \u001b[36mttnn\u001b[0m:\u001b[36m<module>\u001b[0m:\u001b[36m77\u001b[0m - \u001b[34m\u001b[1mInitial ttnn.CONFIG:\r\nConfig{cache_path=/home/ttuser/.cache/ttnn,model_cache_path=/home/ttuser/.cache/ttnn/models,tmp_dir=/tmp/ttnn,enable_model_cache=false,enable_fast_runtime_mode=true,throw_exception_on_fallback=false,enable_logging=false,enable_graph_report=false,enable_detailed_buffer_report=false,enable_detailed_tensor_report=false,enable_comparison_mode=false,comparison_mode_should_raise_exception=false,comparison_mode_pcc=0.9999,root_report_path=generated/ttnn/reports,report_name=std::nullopt,std::nullopt}\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.262445, "o", "╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n║  ZORK I on Tenstorrent QB2 RISC-V via Python / ttnn    ║\r\n║  1977 Gaming Technology on 2026 AI Accelerator Silicon  ║\r\n╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
